OL,3,CResident doctors in England call off
OL,4,Cstrike action after government offer
OL,6,FResident doctors in England have
OL,7,Fcalled off strike action after the
OL,8,Fgovernment made a new offer which will
OL,9,Fbe put to members.
OL,11,FThey were set to stage a four-day
OL,12,Fwalkout from 7am on Monday, which
OL,13,Fwould have been the 16th round of
OL,14,Fstrike action since 2023.
OL,16,FBut the British Medical Association
OL,17,F(BMA) said on Saturday that a last-
OL,18,Fminute offer had been made, which will
OL,19,Fbe put to members.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
