OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781387267
OL,3,CResident doctors in England call off
OL,4,Cstrike action after government offer
OL,6,FDr Jack Fletcher, chairman of the
OL,7,FBMA's resident doctors committee
OL,8,F(RDC), said: "We have always been
OL,9,Fclear that no strikes needed to go
OL,10,Fahead if we received an offer
OL,11,Fappropriate to put to our members.
OL,13,F"This should not have been left to the
OL,14,Flast moment, but we hold up our end of
OL,15,Fthe bargain when the government shifts
OL,16,Fits position."
OL,26,@pD@NOUuD@AOUxD@NO]
