OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781387267
OL,3,CResident doctors in England call off
OL,4,Cstrike action after government offer
OL,6,F"All we have asked for is a fair offer
OL,7,Fthat secures enough jobs to tackle the
OL,8,Fmadness of doctor unemployment and
OL,9,Ftake steps to address the erosion of
OL,10,Four pay.
OL,12,F"Tens of thousands of frontline
OL,13,Fdoctors will now vote in a referendum
OL,14,Fon whether this offer is sufficient.
OL,16,F"We will always negotiate in good
OL,17,Ffaith and strikes are a last resort
OL,18,Fthat we will only use in the face of
OL,19,Fcomplete government intransigence.
OL,20,FWhen government moves, so do we.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
