PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781387267
OL,3,CResident doctors in England call off
OL,4,Cstrike action after government offer
OL,6,F"Doctors will now have their say. If
OL,7,Fthey say no to this offer, we will
OL,8,Fhave to continue our plans for further
OL,9,Fescalated action across next month."
